'''Bic Cristal'''（或稱'''Bic Pen'''）是由法國公司{{le|Société Bic|Société Bic}}生產的一种廉價一次性[[原子筆|原子筆]]，於1950年12月面世。2006年9月，Bic Cristal銷量達到1000億支後，隨即被[[金氏世界紀錄|金氏世界紀錄]]認證為世界上最暢銷的筆。Bic Cristal的六邊形設計源於經典的鉛筆外形。此外，Bic Cristal被認為是典型和「無處不在」的原子筆<ref name="Smithsonian">{{cite news|url=http://www.smithsonianmag.com/arts-culture/universal-typeface-averages-worlds-handwriting-to-produce-an-incredibly-average-font-180951904/|title=The Universal Typeface Project Averages the World's Handwriting to Produce an Incredibly Average Font|last=Stamp|first=Jimmy|work=Smithsonian|access-date=2017-03-15|language=en|archive-date=2017-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170316024225/http://www.smithsonianmag.com/arts-culture/universal-typeface-averages-worlds-handwriting-to-produce-an-incredibly-average-font-180951904/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，甚至[[現代藝術博物館|現代藝術博物館]]也將其列為永久性館藏。

==歷史==
1944年[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]接近尾聲時，商人{{le|馬塞爾·比蓋|Marcel Bich}}於法國北部郊區[[上塞纳省|上塞纳省]][[克利希_(上塞纳省)|克利希]]买下了一所工廠<ref name=timeline>{{cite web|title=Our Heritage, Your Passion|url=https://www.bicworld.com/en/about-us/our-heritage-your-passion|website=BICWorld|accessdate=2017-05-01|language=en|archive-date=2017-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308184759/http://www.bicworld.com/en/about-us/our-heritage-your-passion|dead-url=no}}</ref>。並與他的商業夥伴愛德華·比法爾（Edouard Buffard）於1945年成立了公司Société PPA（即現今的Société Bic）。「PPA」代表筆杆、自動鉛筆和配件（Porte-plume, Porte-mines et Accessoires）。

[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]期間，比蓋於[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]見識到由[[比羅·拉斯洛|比羅·拉斯洛]]製造的原子筆。1949年至1950年間，Société PPA的設計團隊「Décolletage Plastique」設計出Bic Cristal<ref name="Phaidon">{{cite book|author1=Editors of Phaidon|editor1-last=Fletcher|editor1-first=Alan|title={{tsl|en|Phaidon Design Classics||Phaidon Design Classics}} – Volume 2|date=2006|publisher=Phaidon Press|location=London|isbn=0-7148-4399-7|edition=1. publ.}}</ref><ref name="Humble">{{cite web|title=Humble Masterpieces|url=https://www.moma.org/momaorg/shared/pdfs/docs/explore/exhibitions/humble_checklist.pdf|publisher=[[現代藝術博物館|The Museum of Modern Art]]|accessdate=2017-03-13|location=New York|date=2004-09-27|archive-date=2021-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210830174532/https://www.moma.org/momaorg/shared/pdfs/docs/explore/exhibitions/humble_checklist.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。團隊投資的瑞士技術可將能夠成型的金屬壓至{{convert|0.01|mm}}，生產出{{convert|1|mm}}的一個不銹鋼球體，讓墨水能夠自由地流動<ref name="PhaidonOnline">{{cite web|title=Everyday Icon #3 The BIC Biro  {{!}} Design {{!}} Agenda {{!}} Phaidon|url=http://au.phaidon.com/agenda/design/articles/2011/october/19/everyday-icon-3-the-bic-biro/|website=Phaidon|accessdate=2017-05-16|archive-date=2013-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515052501/http://au.phaidon.com/agenda/design/articles/2011/october/19/everyday-icon-3-the-bic-biro/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。比蓋及他的團隊更開發了一種[[粘度|粘度]]的油墨，既不洩漏也不堵塞。在獲得[[比羅·拉斯洛|比羅·拉斯洛]]許可的原子筆專利的保護下，於1950年12月正式推出Bic Cristal<ref name="Phaidon"/>。

比蓋積極向廣告方面投放資金，並於1952年聘請海報設計師{{le|雷蒙德·薩維尼亞克|Raymond Savignac}}，同年獲得法國奧斯卡廣告大獎<ref name=timeline/>。1953年，廣告主管Pierre Guichenné建議比蓋將他的姓氏“Bich”的缩写“Bic”作為[[商品名|商品名]]，因为它便于记忆，容易在全球范围内被接受，符合戰後時代的產品品牌名稱的流行趨勢<ref name="PhaidonOnline"/>。而比蓋的公司之廣告初期將''Cristal''稱為原子筆<ref>{{cite book|last1=Rota|first1=Matt|title=The Art of Ballpoint: Experimentation, Exploration, and Techniques in Ink|publisher=Rockport Publishers|isbn=978-1-63159-057-3|page=12|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=s4aqCgAAQBAJ|accessdate=2017-03-26|language=en|quote=An early BIC ad campaign referred to the pen as the 'Atomic Pen.'}}</ref>。

1959年，比蓋將Bic Cristal帶進美國市場，並推出新口號「一次寫，次次寫」（Writes first time, every time），原子筆售價約29[[分_(貨幣)|分]]（{{inflation|US|0.29|1959|r=2|fmt=eq|cursign=$}}）<ref name="first">{{cite news |url=http://articles.courant.com/1995-07-04/features/9507080125_1_new-dollar-dollar-coin-eisenhower-dollar |title=Who Says $1 Dollar Won't Buy Anything Anymore |last=Larcen |first=Donna |newspaper={{tsl|en|The Hartford Courant||The Hartford Courant}} |date=1995-07-04 |accessdate=2014-06-30 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714221426/http://articles.courant.com/1995-07-04/features/9507080125_1_new-dollar-dollar-coin-eisenhower-dollar |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1965年，[[法國教育部|法國教育部]]（Ministère de l'Éducation nationale et de la Jeunesse）正式批准Bic Cristal用於學校課室<ref name="guardian">{{cite web|last1=Smith|first1=David|title=It's 70 today, but our favourite pen just keeps rolling along|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2008/jun/15/news|website=The Guardian|date=2008-06-14|access-date=2020-08-04|archive-date=2021-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524194632/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2008/jun/15/news|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2006年9月，在銷量達至1000億支後，Bic Cristal被[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]认证為世界上最暢銷的筆<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/pen-best-selling/ |title=Pen – best selling |publisher=Guinness World Records |date=2006-01-09 |accessdate=2016-02-13 |archive-date=2016-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160217021732/http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/pen-best-selling/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==原子筆設計==
[[File:4_Bic_Cristal_pens_and_caps.jpg|thumb]]

Bic Cristal的[[工業設計|工業設計]]獲得[[現代藝術博物館|現代藝術博物館]]的認可，並引入成為博物館永久性館藏<ref name="Humble"/><ref name=MoMA>{{cite web |url=http://www.moma.org/collection/browse_results.php?object_id=82141 |title=Bic Cristal in MoMA collection |publisher=Moma.org |date= |accessdate=2013-08-04 |archive-date=2013-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130830234749/http://www.moma.org/collection/browse_results.php?object_id=82141 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它的[[六邊形|六邊形]]形狀類似於原始木製鉛筆，能夠承托使用者寫字時手部所施加的壓力和寫字時手部和原子筆形成三個握點，使書寫時更穩定。此外，原子筆藏有透明[[聚苯乙烯|聚苯乙烯]]桶及[[聚丙烯|聚丙烯]]管，以顯示墨水量<ref name="Phaidon"/>。唯一的例外是BIC Cristal UP，這是Bic銷售的一支筆，聲稱使用時可以形成更清晰的線條。這些筆的筆桿是白色的，根據儲墨器所含的顏色，筆桿和筆帽的一小塊區域會有相應的墨水顏色。筒上有一個小孔，讓筆內及筆外保持相同的氣壓<ref name="faq">{{cite web|title=FAQ – BIC AU Website|url=http://au.bicworld.com/faq.html|website=au.bicworld.com|accessdate=2017-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170426202931/http://au.bicworld.com/faq.html|archive-date=2017-04-26|7=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。筆的墨水顏色種類繁多，除了有典型原子筆墨水顏色（藍、黑、紅、綠）之外，也有粉色及紫色。濃稠的墨水由於[[毛細現象|毛細現象]]從筆筒內部的管子流下來，送入球軸承，球軸承在[[黃銅|黃銅]]筆尖內自由旋轉<ref name="Ohio">{{cite web|last1=Lemon|first1=Michael|title=Bic Cristal Pens {{!}} The World's Most Popular Pen|url=https://u.osu.edu/bicpens/|website=OSU.EDU|publisher=Ohio State University|accessdate=2017-03-26|date=2015-04-28|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106004548/https://u.osu.edu/bicpens/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1961年，[[不銹鋼球|不銹鋼球]]被更硬的[[碳化鎢|碳化鎢]]取代。原子筆首先經過{{le|高溫陶化|vitrified}}，然後在塗有[[钻石|工業金剛石]]磨料的旋轉板之間進行研磨，精度達到{{convert|0.1|µm|in|abbr=on}}<ref name="Ohio"/>。原本的笔帽因为一端是堵住的，誤吞的話可能会堵塞氣道导致窒息，所以1991年起，該筆的流線型筆帽末端加上一個小孔。即使误吞也不会导致窒息<ref name="Phaidon"/><ref name=faq/>。另外筆帽又改用[[聚丙烯|聚丙烯]]代替[[聚苯乙烯|聚苯乙烯]]，全因它可以更好地吸收衝擊力，從而降低了筆掉落到筆帽時破裂的風險<ref name="Ohio"/>。

笔連筆帽的尺寸为{{convert|5+7/8|x|1/2|in|cm}}。不連筆帽則14.5乘0.7[[釐米|-{zh-cn:厘米;zh-hk:釐米;zh-tw:公分;}-]]<ref name=MoMA/> 。

Bic Cristal的設計成為造假者的目标，主要來自遠東以及中國一帶的造假者挪用Bic Cristal設計<ref name="kenya">{{cite web|last1=Waka|first1=Brenda|title=RESPONSE STRATEGIES OF HACO INDUSTRIES KENYA LIMITED TO THE CHALLENGES OF COUNTERFEIT PRODUCTS IN EAST AFRICA|url=http://erepository.uonbi.ac.ke/bitstream/handle/11295/21841/Waka_Response%20Strategies%20of%20Haco%20Industries%20Kenya%20Limited%20to%20the%20Challenges%20of%20Counterfeit%20Products%20in%20East%20Africa.pdf|website=University of Nairobi Digital Repository|publisher=Haco Industries Kenya Limited|accessdate=2017-04-21|archive-date=2021-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210830174425/http://erepository.uonbi.ac.ke/bitstream/handle/11295/21841/Waka_Response%20Strategies%20of%20Haco%20Industries%20Kenya%20Limited%20to%20the%20Challenges%20of%20Counterfeit%20Products%20in%20East%20Africa.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他們的翻版筆批發價格比較便宜，做出來的外觀和原來的差不多。一所肯尼亞鋼筆製造商因假貨而損失了1億[[肯尼亞先令|肯尼亞先令]]（按2009年匯率計算約合130萬美元），迫使他們與Bic公司談判更便宜的生產許可證<ref name="kenya"/>。

== 衍生產品 ==

===Bic Cristal for Her===
2012年，Société Bic推出Bic Cristal的衍生產品「Bic Cristal for Her」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Vinjamuri|first1=David|title=Bic For Her: What They Were Actually Thinking (As Told By A Man Who Worked On Tampons)|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/davidvinjamuri/2012/08/30/bic-for-her-what-they-were-actually-thinking-as-told-by-a-man-who-worked-on-tampons|website=Forbes|accessdate=2017-04-17|archive-date=2017-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170418085507/https://www.forbes.com/sites/davidvinjamuri/2012/08/30/bic-for-her-what-they-were-actually-thinking-as-told-by-a-man-who-worked-on-tampons/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，新產品与原版类似，但针对女性进行了特别设计，能让女性握感舒适，并以「顏色柔和，閃閃發光」作亮點<ref>{{Cite web |title=Bic for Her – pens designed for women. – Virtual tour of Museum of Failure |url=https://collection.museumoffailure.com/bic-for-her-pens-designed-for-women/ |accessdate=2020-08-01 |work=失敗博物館 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108160651/https://collection.museumoffailure.com/bic-for-her-pens-designed-for-women/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。唯Bic Cristal for Her在互聯網上被廣泛批評及嘲笑，例如於[[亞馬遜公司|Amazon.com]]的客戶評論部分裏<ref>{{cite web|last1=News|first1=ABC|title=Bic Pens 'For Her' Draw Amazon Flames|url=https://abcnews.go.com/blogs/headlines/2012/08/bic-pens-for-her-draw-amazon-flames/|website=ABC News|accessdate=2017-04-17|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423062546/https://abcnews.go.com/blogs/headlines/2012/08/bic-pens-for-her-draw-amazon-flames/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此產品更被[[失敗博物館|失敗博物館]]收集並作館藏<ref>{{cite news|title=At This Museum, Failures Are Welcome|first1=Christine|last1=Hauser|first2=Christina|last2=Anderson|date=2017-04-21|newspaper=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/25/arts/museum-of-failure.html|accessdate=2020-08-04|archive-date=2020-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200621020821/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/25/arts/museum-of-failure.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== Cristal Stylus ===
2014，Bic在Cristal的基础上推出了新产品「Cristal Stylus」。新款的筆尖使用了膠頭而不是滚珠，用於在[[觸控板|觸控板]]上书写<ref>{{cite news|last1=Liszewski|first1=Andrew|title=The Classic Bic Pen Now Works On Your Smartphone Display Too|url=https://gizmodo.com/the-classic-bic-pen-now-works-on-your-smartphone-displa-1510693371|accessdate=2017-03-17|work=Gizmodo|date=2014-01-28|archive-date=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306023005/https://gizmodo.com/the-classic-bic-pen-now-works-on-your-smartphone-displa-1510693371|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Société Bic还投资了一个用于推广Cristal Stylus的网站，用戶可使用Crystal Stylus配合觸摸板在網站上輸入手寫體，手寫體名為{{le|通用字體實驗|Universal Typeface Experiment}}<ref name=Smithsonian/>。

